  <h1>CSV Parser</h1>
  <p class="hint">Paste CSV into the box below. Supports commas inside quotes, escaped quotes (""), and newlines inside quoted fields.</p>

  <textarea id="csvInput" placeholder='Example:
Name,Age,Note
"Smith, John",30,"Line1
Line2"
"Jane ""JJ"" Doe",25,"He said ""Hello, world!"""
'></textarea>

  <div class="controls">
